{"tid":503852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日推測北海道30年內或有8.8級以上強震","createTime":"2017-12-19T09:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T10:55:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"12b74813bca806b6ec4ad410f76d3c05f7140f48","tid":503852,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"日本政府地震調查委員會今日公布最新評估報告，指位於北海道海域的千島海溝，未來30年內發生8.8級或以上強震的機率，高達7%至40%，震源區域更可能擴大至建有大量核電相關設施的青森縣沿岸區域。內閣府料在明年公布新的北海道地震損毀評估。<br />\n<br />\n地震調查委員會表示，千島海溝一帶過往平均每340至380年，就會發生一次這種程度的超強地震，但對上一次發生距今已長達約400年，故再次發生的時間可能已非常迫切。<br />\n<br />\n委員會以千島海溝附近有3個震源區域作設想，並考慮橫跨震源區域發生地震的情况後，根據各種模擬推算，指今後30年間在北海道東部近海，發生類似400年超強地震的機率介乎7%至40%。北海道大學推算，400年前地震引發的海嘯超過20米，從沿岸起4公里的內陸地區均會被淹沒。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，最新推算的震源區域，更可能擴大至青森縣近海等地，地震規模亦更大。青森縣太平洋沿岸建有大量核電相關設施，地震調查委員會與內閣府將評估超強地震將引發的海嘯高度，及沿岸地區的搖晃強度。<br />\n<br />\n今次是日本政府自2004年以來，首次進行千島海溝的地震長期評估。當局今日亦發布四國地區的最新主要活斷層長期評估，是自2003年以來首次修改有關橫穿該地區「中央構造線斷層帶」的評估，新修改該斷層帶延伸至大分縣，長度從360公里增長至444公里。<br />\n<br />\n（共同社/朝日新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171219/s00005/1513673678545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171219%2Fs00005%2F1513673678545&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1bd2ba04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171219%2Fs00005%2F1513673678545&h=d09af82e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171219/s00005/1513673678545</a>"},{"pid":"280072f87a656926f46a82af56d4ddf3df386307","tid":503852,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"其實地震對腳好似坐地鐵咁企咪唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51bf9bae847ea62cc7b89556d79c13ff6802ec7","tid":503852,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"等睇有人懶叻話&quot;我都預測到xxx年內肯定有xx級地震&quot;"},{"pid":"58e802857f8ad399bd4ecccdce37097e1b24981a","tid":503852,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cb05bb9dd4146b63bc03a818a1988b98d89e0f0","tid":503852,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地震有得預測既咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係低到咁呀話？"},{"pid":"31612d90e6819a4b3f7ec9656e9380d770511db5","tid":503852,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcd2f297842818c8638aacd01a8e9927c25d947","tid":503852,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實地震對腳好似坐地鐵咁企咪唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同你屋企d傢俬雜物講啦"},{"pid":"f2e946327414b633f05ac04773cd7a821f44e017","tid":503852,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"睇錯目測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}